<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الرشتي <span style="color:#707070">[١٢١٢ - ١٢٥٩ هـ / ١٧٩٧ - ١٨٤٣ م]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
